{"tid":1123863,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"戒丁記錄","createTime":"2019-04-24T17:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T11:37:39.000Z","uid":59151,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"65dd38c636078a0cf662c5e0d7faff6c076be18f","tid":1123863,"uid":59151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:04:48.000Z","msg":"唔講乜鳩垃圾野 每日00:00左右上黎報告 講大話既以後冇女生仔冇屎忽（無謂搞埋屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />） 其實之前都開過類似既post架啦 都好似有戒到一個月<br />\n<br />\n開呢個post之前幾乎日日打 睇下戒左之後身體有咩變化會包膠一下 另外順便戒m記 奶茶同啡<br />\n<br />\n目標一個月先<br />\n<br />\nDay0<br />\n<br />\n另外想問如果一月一丁算唔算戒到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPs. 咪貼丁圖 認真 一貼我就會block <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd01b3b82082b499939a37f116b4fec7ac9edc58","tid":1123863,"uid":117346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"咩原因而打丁 壓力定習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ab540208232d6e1e3348d353585d789c895340","tid":1123863,"uid":142826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:08:15.000Z","msg":"Hi 我好難得Day5 啦  <br />\n我之前都試過20日不過三年前<br />\n希望今次我有30日<br />\n撐住吖行街少啲𥄫女返屋企早啲訓/做到自己好忘就應該無野"},{"pid":"b24a68fbbc866b296f6d1c224f4cd44827d3b789","tid":1123863,"uid":43842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:08:31.000Z","msg":"巴打用漸進式戒丁仲好啦<br />\n1d -&gt; 3d -&gt; 7d -&gt; 14d -&gt; 1m -&gt; 2m -&gt; 6m -&gt; 1yr"},{"pid":"bdd4a30e245d54aa7a0b4f9cd43dd753c79f7b15","tid":1123863,"uid":162095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:09:11.000Z","msg":"啱啱戒咗十幾粒鐘，巴打加油"},{"pid":"18488a6f363326e9c4090c36e9e3ca4e34da6a16","tid":1123863,"uid":59151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"dd01b3b82082b499939a37f116b4fec7ac9edc58","tid":1123863,"uid":117346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17: